      <title>印尼称波音公司高管和诺贝尔奖得主持有黄金签证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/indonesia-says-boeing-executive-nobel-winner-hold-golden-visas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼最高移民官员表示，波音公司的一位高级官员和一位诺贝尔奖获得者是印尼黄金签证的早期持有者。该计划自一年前推出以来，已吸引了 300 名申请者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/indonesia-says-boeing-executive-nobel-winner-hold-golden-visas</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 09:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝钢对沙特合资企业投资额增加一倍至10亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/baosteel-doubles-investment-in-saudi-steel-venture-to-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的钢铁生产商宝山钢铁股份有限公司宣布，其在沙特阿拉伯钢板生产企业的投资额已增加一倍多，达到 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/baosteel-doubles-investment-in-saudi-steel-venture-to-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 08:56:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
