      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/drugmakers-gain-steam-as-emphasis-on-new-drugs-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对新型创新药物的关注有助于刺激销售，欧洲大型制药商纷纷上调财务预期。]]></description>
